    public final class OverlapJCasTermAnnotator
extends AbstractJCasTermAnnotator
    Checks for terms that overlap a window. All tokens of the term must exist in the window in order, but not necessarily contiguously Author: SPF Affiliation: CHIP-NLP Date: 12/6/13
